profile:
All Seasons Property Services began as Snownorth Ontario Ltd. in 1998, and is located on Lake Dalrymple. We are a family business that provides repairs & service on small engines & marine vehicles, as well as winter BOAT STORAGE.
Due to a demand in the area, our business has grown to include outdoor property maintenance & in doing so the owner, Bruce Both found another passion. His love of the outdoors & his uncanny ability to spruce things up makes these tasks enjoyable!
We enhance properties with curb appeal & value so our customers can enjoy it & have property to be proud of. As we steadily grow, we continue to provide our customers with the results they need and the service they deserve.
Why you should use All Seasons Property Service:
In business since 1998
Local, family business
Professional, friendly, hardworking & honest
Non-traditional hours; available 24 hours/day, 7 days/week if necessary
Fully Insured
WSIB Coverage
Licensed technicians
Support local clubs; President of Carden SnoDrifters
Volunteer Firefighter of Carden Fire Department
Our service area covers; Sebright, Kawartha Lakes, Bolsover, Brechin, Lagoon City, Bayshore, Atherley & Orillia
